abstract: >-
  Codomyrmex is a modular, AI-native coding workspace with 130 top-level
  modules and 623 production MCP tool decorators. Its current merged runtime
  manifest exposes 608 tools. It provides multi-agent
  orchestration for Claude, Gemini, GPT, and 10+ agent providers,
  integrated with the Personal AI Infrastructure (PAI) via the Model
  Context Protocol.
